title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - USA - Rainbow bridge
description:
In this video we will fly over the Rainbow bridge. The Niagara Falls International Rainbow Bridge, commonly known as the Rainbow Bridge, is an arch bridge across the Niagara River gorge. It connects the cities of Niagara Falls, New York, United States (to the east), and Niagara Falls, Ontario, Canada (west).
